<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background:#f5f7fa; padding: 40px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <table width="520" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background:#ffffff; border-radius:10px; padding: 40px; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333333;">
        
        <!-- Logo -->
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="margin:0; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#0c5ddc;">CertGate</h2>
            <p style="font-size:12px; color:#888;">Trust. Security. Automation.</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Title -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
            <h3 style="margin:0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600; color:#222;">이메일 인증을 완료해주세요</h3>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Message -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding-bottom: 28px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#555;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0;">
              안녕하세요, <strong><%= @user.name || @user.email %></strong> 님 👋
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
              CertGate 계정 생성을 완료하려면 아래 인증 버튼을 클릭해주세요.
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0;">
              보안을 위해 이 링크는 <strong>1회용</strong>입니다.
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Button -->
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 25px;">
            <a href="<%= confirm_user_url(token: @user.confirmation_token) %>" 
               style="background:#0c5ddc; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; padding:14px 28px; 
                      border-radius:6px; font-size:16px; font-weight:600; display:inline-block;">
              이메일 인증하기
            </a>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Sub Message -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding-bottom: 25px; font-size:14px; color:#777; line-height:1.5;">
            <p style="margin:0;">
              버튼이 동작하지 않는다면 아래 링크를 복사해 브라우저 주소창에 붙여넣기 해주세요:
            </p>
            <p style="font-size:12px; color:#0c5ddc; word-break:break-all; margin-top:8px;">
              <%= confirm_user_url(token: @user.confirmation_token) %>
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="padding-top: 10px; border-top:1px solid #e5e8ec; font-size:12px; color:#999;">
            <p style="margin: 15px 0 0 0;">본 이메일은 CertGate 자동 알림 시스템에서 발송되었습니다.</p>
            <p style="margin:5px 0;">Copyright © <%= Time.current.year %> CertGate. All Rights Reserved.</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>